cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.IR, cs.MM

This paper involves the development of a deep learning system for mammogram analysis, which falls under computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG) sub-categories. The system also involves clinical decision support, which can be categorized under artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and information retrieval (cs.IR). Finally, the paper deals with medical imaging, which can be classified under multimedia (cs.MM) sub-category.
